WEBVTT

00:05.322 --> 00:07.189
I'm not gonna sugarcoat this.

00:07.191 --> 00:10.275
Only some of you
are gonna get this job.

00:10.277 --> 00:12.361
It's a business
of broken hearts.

00:12.363 --> 00:15.480
But you know that...
you're professionals.

00:16.617 --> 00:18.650
They're so cute! I just want

00:18.652 --> 00:20.836
to eat your little faces off!

00:21.838 --> 00:23.505
Oh, don't worry, I won't.

00:23.507 --> 00:24.556
Okay, babies,

00:24.558 --> 00:26.091
for the purpose
of this audition,

00:26.093 --> 00:29.761
you're babies, wearing our
client's cute little outfits.

00:29.763 --> 00:32.162
And... action.

00:37.738 --> 00:38.971
And scene.

00:38.973 --> 00:40.439
Many of you were very good.

00:40.441 --> 00:41.773
You, sir, were dogging it.

00:41.775 --> 00:43.525
You know you were.
Yeah.

00:43.527 --> 00:44.643
Look at him.

00:44.645 --> 00:46.028
Someone has baby fever.

00:46.030 --> 00:47.696
Guilty.
Our creative director,

00:47.698 --> 00:49.398
my daughter,
is in a promising relationship,

00:49.400 --> 00:52.451
and I hope that one of you
is in my near future.

00:52.453 --> 00:54.536
And auditions like these
will be unnecessary,

00:54.538 --> 00:56.622
because clearly
I'm a big fan of nepotism.

00:57.400 --> 00:59.241
Hey, piglet, how about
you and me truffle hunt.

00:59.243 --> 01:00.409
Come on, now.

